net.sf.mmm.util.reflect.api

Class ClassName

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.mmm.util.reflect.api.ClassName

  • public class ClassName
extends Object
    This is a simple identifier for a Class. Unlike Class it can also identify non existent classes (e.g. that should be generated). On the other hand passing the qualified classname as String around for such purpose may lead to additional parsing e.g. to extract the simple name.
    Since:
    3.0.0
    Author:
    Joerg Hohwiller (hohwille at users.sourceforge.net)
